data.text:
The trainer's room is set up to make sure that Wayland's athletic trainer can keep our student-athletes in tip top shapeâ€”equipped with a hot/iced bath, trainer's table, workstation, and storage units.

Our coaches need a place of respite from the stress of competition to gather their thoughts and store their belongings during a game. The Coaches' Locker Room is a perfect space for a coach to have some time alone or to consult with their assistant coach before addressing their team.
